  "short_description": "Slug Wars is an online multiplayer 3rd-person shooter, where you play as cute Slugs, and after being eliminated you get to choose a power up! Slug Wars has been designed to be more approachable entry to the shooting game genre, and for the best experience we recommend playing with your friends!",
